-- Aluminum Usage in Cars Forecast to Rise to 160 KG by 2020
-- B y   A g n i e s z k a   T r o s z k i e w i c z
-- 2013-09-18T15:54:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-09-18/aluminum-usage-in-cars-forecast-to-rise-to-160-kg-by-2020.html
Aluminum usage in cars will avg.
160kg/car by 2020 vs 140 kg/car in 2012, Werner Stelzer, a
former Alcan executive who is an automotive and aluminum
consultant in  Switzerland , says in presentation for the Metal
Bulletin aluminum conference in Geneva today.
